This issue has been repeated in CI, but not manually. On the above machine I was not able to reproduce by hand. 
Manual tests include:
-Ran the following 100 successful attach/detach attempts on an instance-store backed instance using eutester:
{code}
print vols
    [Volume:vol-6306ca6d, Volume:vol-3fcb545c]
for x in xrange(0,20):
    for vol in vols:
        ins.attach_volume(vol)
    for vol in vols:
        ins.detach_euvolume(vol
{code}

-Ran the following roughly 50 times with no failures:
{code}
emi = tester.get_emi(root_device_type='ebs')
key = tester.get_all_current_local_keys()[0]
grp = tester.add_group('default')
for x in xrange(0,100):
    ins = tester.run_image(emi,zone='one',  group=grp,keypair=key, min=1, max=1, private_addressing=True, timeout=600 )[0]
    ins.stop_instance_and_verify()
    time.sleep(5)
    ins.start_instance_and_verify()
    ins.terminate_and_verify()
{code}
